data.title: Victoria's Secret boyfriends & husbands: Meet the men behind the wings
data.meta_description: Victoria's Secret boyfriends and husbands of the angels: How did they meet their VS ladies? What are their hobbies? What do they do (outside of being the other half of some of the most beautiful women on the planet)? Read more on GLAMOUR (UK).
data.text:
What sort of guy do you have to be to bag yourself a Victoria's Secret Angel? It's the question most men would secretly give their right leg to know the answer to...

Despite their fame – having bagged the most coveted modelling jobs in the industry – there are still some Victoria's Secret boyfriends, fiancees and husbands that we know very little about. There's rockstars, athletes, fellow models (naturally), and even one senior advisor to the President of the United States...

For example, did you know that Alessandra Ambrosio has a new beau after splitting from her partner of a decade, Jamie Mazur? What about Karlie Kloss's ties to the White House (yes, really) via her husband Josh Kushner? And which Angel do you think said these words, upon meeting her rock star partner at Coachella back in 2007 – "He was performing and as soon as I saw him, I couldn't stop thinking about him"?

But perhaps the sweetest of all Victoria's Secret model couplings is that between Dutch Angel Romee Strijd and her longterm boyfriend Laurens Van Leeuwen, who is also, coincidentally, a Dutch model. Despite only being 24 and 29 years old respectively, Romee and Laurens are ultimate couple goals, having reportedly been together for around ten years and knowing each other since they were teenagers – adorable!

So, how did these BFs meet their VS ladies? What's their story, and what do they do (outside of being the other half of some of the most beautiful women on the planet, makeup or not)? Well don't worry, because we've done the digging and found out everything you need to know about the world's most attractive pairings.
